*Imamo* mnogo društvenih aktivnosti. (We have a lot of social activities.)

*Imam*o četiri psa. (We have four dogs.)

*Imali* smo priliku da putujemo. (We had an opportunity to travel.)

*Imaju*ćemo svoje vlasništvo. (We will have our own property.)

*Imaj*te na umu da se mora raditi. (Keep in mind that work must be done.)